Value.Comment: For my beloved children: Briana, Laura, Kainan, Sara, Andrew and Nathan.
Even "Darkness" may hold more beauty than the so called, "Light".
Audi loquacem vulturem, qui neutiquam te decipit. Ego sum niger albus citrinus et rubeus.
Thank you Kevin & Tammy (Dad, Mom) for always supporting & encouraging my artistic side! Love you.
Thank you Koji Igarashi and everyone involved over the years for all the amazing games and memories.
Stars, hide your fires; Let not light see my black and deep desires.
